title: SC EP:351 Dark Waters
itunes:title: SC EP:351 Dark Waters
description:
My guest tonight is Dark Waters and he will be sharing with us some encounters he has not shared with anyone. Join me as I welcome DW to the show. Check out Dark Waters on Facebook and YouTube  

I will also be welcoming to the show Bob Gimlin and Russell Acord to the show to talk about Bob’s new documentary. Follow-up with news on Bob at www.bobgimlin.net
